articles.title: Source -- Ex-Alabama star safety Caleb Downs picks Ohio State - ESPN
articles.description: Former Alabama safety Caleb Downs, a second-team All-American as a true freshman last season and ESPN's No. 1-ranked player in the transfer portal, has committed to Ohio State, a source told ESPN.
articles.content:
Former Alabama freshman safety Caleb Downs is transferring to Ohio State, a source told ESPN on Friday night.
